# Reversing Passwords

## QWORD Challenge

Assembly:

```asm
movabs rbx,0x7334547a62415538
cmp rax,rbx
```

Python:

```python
print(0x7334547a62415538.to_bytes(8,"little").decode())
```

Output:

```text
8UAbzT4s
```

---

## DWORD Challenge

Assembly:

```asm
cmp eax,0x4e457236
cmp eax,0x52594e56
cmp eax,0x69363270
cmp eax,0x4b367764
```

Python:

```python
print(
    (
        0x4e457236.to_bytes(4,"little") +
        0x52594e56.to_bytes(4,"little") +
        0x69363270.to_bytes(4,"little") +
        0x4b367764.to_bytes(4,"little")
    ).decode()
)
```

