# Scrambled Struct Solver Template

```python
pw = bytearray(16)

pw[0:8]   = VALUE1.to_bytes(8,"little")
pw[8:12]  = VALUE2.to_bytes(4,"little")
pw[12:14] = VALUE3.to_bytes(2,"little")
